title: Instant Pot Hard Boiled Eggs
summary: If you have about 15 minutes to spend in the kitchen, Instant Pot Hard Boiled Eggs might be a great gluten free, dairy free, paleolithic, and lacto ovo vegetarian recipe to try. This recipe serves 12 and costs 24 cents per serving. One serving contains 63 calories, 6g of protein, and 4g of fat. It works well as a side dish. If you have eggs, ice, water, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. This recipe is liked by 9128 foodies and cooks. It is brought to you by Cooking with Curls. Overall, this recipe earns a rather bad spoonacular score of 27%.
